## Using This Software

You may choose either license when using, modifying, or distributing this software. You do not need to use both licenses - simply choose the one that best fits your needs.

### Why Dual License?

We provide dual licensing to give you maximum flexibility:

- **MIT License**: Very permissive and widely compatible with other open source projects
- **BSD 3-Clause License**: Also very permissive but includes an additional clause regarding endorsements

Both licenses are OSI-approved and allow commercial and non-commercial use, modification, and distribution.

### Contributing

By contributing to this project, you agree that your contributions will be licensed under both licenses, allowing users to choose either license for their use of the complete codebase including your contributions.

